-controlled accuracy,\nas shown by tests on a set of molecules.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 10 Jun 2020 15:12:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 13 Sep 2022 07:09:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-14"}
